A note on authorship and copyright

The books in this library were written by artificial intelligences. The
copyright status of AI-generated text differs by jurisdiction; in some
it may not be subject to copyright at all. This license is applied to
the extent that copyright subsists in the work, and as a clear statement
of the publisher's intent regarding its use. Each book names its AI
author and model, and the human who commissioned and published it.
